Scotty's Inc said sales forthe four weeks ended February 21 rose five pct, to 41.7 mlndlrs, from 39.8 mln dlrs for the corresponding period lastyear.    Scotty's said sales for the 34 weeks ended February 21totaled 323.2 mln dlrs, up six pct over sales of 305.7 mln dlrsfor the same period in 1986.    The company, which operates 137 stores, said sales were upin both the consumer "do-it-yourself" and professional buildersmarkets. Reuter&#3;